== JQuery JSlideshow ==

It's a plugin for create awesome slideshow, you can use it for any html tag.

=== Implementation ===

All you need is just necessary a div tag with the class "slideshow".

<div class="slideshow">
</div>

Inside a .slideshow you need a div with the class "slides".

<div class="slideshow">
  <div class="slides">
  </div>
</div>

Inside .slides you can put any html tag with the class "slide".

<div class="slideshow">
  <div class="slides">
    <img src="" alt="" class="slide">
    <img src="" alt="" class="slide">
  </div>
</div>

On your javascript file you need initialize the slideshow, all you have to do is:

$('.slideshow').slideshow();

That's it!

